main event: A civilian reported observing a solid object reflecting light in Kettering, Ohio on April 16, 1966, for 30 seconds.
interesting points: The object appeared to fade into darkness as it passed overhead., The edges of the object were noted to be fuzzy or blurred., The sighting lasted for a brief 30 seconds., No physical evidence was found to confirm the sighting., The conclusion of the report suggests that it was likely a conventional aircraft.
